    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Combine</strong> the turkey mince and breadcrumbs with 1-2 tbsp olive oil and season generously with salt and pepper</p>\r\n<p><strong>Mix</strong> with clean hands, cover and refrigerate for 15 min</p>\r\n<p>Tip: Chilling the mixture helps the burgers to hold their shape better</p>",
