    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Add</strong> 1-2 tsp olive oil to a pot over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once</strong> hot, add the sliced red onion and the cranberries and cook for 2 min</p>\r\n<p><strong>Add</strong> 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">(300ml)</span> boiling water</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cook</strong> for 15-20 min or until most of the water is absorbed</p>",
