      "instruction": "<p><strong>Combine</strong> the mayonnaise and vinegar with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">(2 tbsp)</span> olive oil and a pinch of salt and pepper in a bowl large enough for the slaw</p>\r\n<p><strong>Grate</strong> the Brussels sprouts, apple and the remaining red onion into the bowl</p>\r\n<p><strong>Stir</strong> well to combine - this is your slaw</p>",
